metadata.name: SOULS
metadata.description: What do you feel when you find a person who is close to you in terms of worldview and to whom you can tell about all your emotional experiences? You bare your heart to him and let him into your soul. Stable and personal disinterested relationships are born between you, which are based on sympathy, common interests, spiritual closeness and mutual affection. Your souls begin to be related. It's a big miracle if you have such person. Take care of each other
